Api using = Pokeapi.co

Pokemon app wtih Pokemon Api

- Welcome the user
- Ask if they'd like to explore the world of pokemon
- If user inputs yes, ask user what pokemon they'd like to learn about. 
-If User selects no the say goodbye to user
- Show species and/or moves and/or form. 
- Ask user if they would like to search for another pokemon. 
- If user responds yes, ask for number will return if user responds no exit screen.

CLI class - deals with the things showing onto the terminal
API class - Deal with all API things
Pokemon class - will deal with all Pokemon

